data.name: PhotoGram
data.description: Which by the name gives us an idea about the app. We can upload photos from our gallery and the content can be viewed in the modal-view and it gets stored in the backend. We can also delete the photos from the app.

data.name: Diary Keeper
data.description: Which is very handy nowadays since we can write all our notes in one single place and it gets stored in the backend as well. This diary app performs CRUD

data.name: Chat App
data.description: Your messaging app where we can login with google, Add a group of your own and start messaging with people in different groups. The groups can be deleted as well.

data.name: Entertainment Adda
data.description: Your one place for all all movies and series. You can search any movies or series with all its details available on the content displayed. Carousel mode is used to display the cast. Trailer of the displayed movie/series is also shown.

data.name: Project Planner
data.description: Your notebook for projects, projects can be created with content written in it and all the projects get displayed. A small To-do app is also displayed so as to write down any important task. All the projects are stored in the firebase and todo is stored in the local storage.
